s a sacrifice to the Alpaca Gods in the Alpos Tower.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572510/extras/97b18c9d21fee5876dcb9064e8193242.poster.avif?t=1726389979\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572510/extras/97b18c9d21fee5876dcb9064e8193242.webm?t=1726389979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572510/extras/97b18c9d21fee5876dcb9064e8193242.mp4?t=1726389979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572510/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1726389979\" width=616 height=1 /></span>",
